  "remarks": "Listing: Instrument of first listing - Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 Listing 2015 (No 1) [F2021L00640, Gazette C2015G00267]. The Minister for Foreign Affairs listed this entity on 24 February 2015 under subsection 15(1) of the Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 (CotUNA), pursuant to Australia's obligations under UNSC resolution 1373 (2001).  The Minister declared on 8 February 2018 and subsequently on 12 October 2020 pursuant to subsection 15A(2) of CotUNA, that this listing would continue to have effect. The Minister listed this entity afresh on 11 October 2023.",
